                <li class=" scale-100 transition-all hover:scale-110"><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kely-mÃ¤tzler-23b1a4301/" target="_blank"><Image src="/icons/LinkedIn.svg" alt="LinkedIn Logo" width={40} height={40} /></a></li>
